      <h1>Germany must 'de-risk' by expanding cooperation</h1>
      <h2></h2>
      <div class="info">
        <span class="info_l">
          By Chen Weihua | 
          China Daily |
          Updated: 2024-04-19 07:23
        </span>
        <span class="info_r">
          <a title="facebook" style="cursor:pointer; " target="_blank" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?title=Germany must &#39;de-risk&#39; by expanding cooperation&amp;u=https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/a/202404/19/WS6621ab5ca31082fc043c2cc8.html"><img src="https://www.chinadaily.com.cn/image_e/2020/facebook.png" height="17px" /></a>
